### WeChat login (mock mode)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/wechat/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "mock:demo_openid:demo_unionid",
  "displayName": "小程序测试用户"
}

### MP wiki list
GET http://localhost:3000/api/mp/wiki?category=all&page=1&limit=5

### MP create post
POST http://localhost:3000/api/mp/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "小程序发帖联调",
  "section": "music",
  "content": "来自小程序接口的首条内容",
  "tags": ["mp", "wechat"]
}

### MP create comment
POST http://localhost:3000/api/mp/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "postId": "REPLACE_POST_ID",
  "content": "这是来自 mp 的评论",
  "parentId": null
}
